ContentDesc_Der Nabel: Having passed the seemingly endless trials imposed upon you by the Company of Heroes, you have been entrusted with the knowledge of a secret way into the Navel, the domain of the primal Titan. Courtesy of Y'shtola's magicks, the beastman aetheryte is now primed to send you to a confrontation with the Lord of Crags. Gird your loins for a struggle of titanic proportions.
Instancecontenttextdata_19310_Text: Tremble before the might of the earth!
Instancecontenttextdata_19311_Text: Sons of man! Murderers of my children!
Instancecontenttextdata_19312_Text: For thee my hatred is unending, unyielding!
Instancecontenttextdata_3800_Text: Sons of man! Murderers of my children!
Instancecontenttextdata_3801_Text: For thee my hatred is unending, unyielding!
Instancecontenttextdata_3802_Text: Tremble before the might of the earth!
Instancecontenttextdata_3803_Text: To the last, I grapple with thee!
Instancecontenttextdata_3804_Text: I shall grind thee beneath my heel, mortal!
Instancecontenttextdata_3805_Text: Hie, my children, into the dark! He will not be denied...
